{"tid":1513558,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【香港狗狗你地仆硬街了】公安部部長趙克志出聲了","createTime":"2019-08-28T11:24:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T11:45:05.000Z","uid":54337,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"00d97a8040846ecfd6b668f5ad597ab952e86939","tid":1513558,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:24:33.000Z","msg":"公安部長廣東考察 強調全力做好建國70年慶典安保維穩工作 2019-08-28 17:06<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/greaterchina/5d664409e60383421f678e41/%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E9%83%A8%E9%95%B7%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E8%80%83%E5%AF%9F-%E5%BC%B7%E8%AA%BF%E5%85%A8%E5%8A%9B%E5%81%9A%E5%A5%BD%E5%BB%BA%E5%9C%8B70%E5%B9%B4%E6%85%B6%E5%85%B8%E5%AE%89%E4%BF%9D%E7%B6%AD%E7%A9%A9%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fgreaterchina%2F5d664409e60383421f678e41%2F%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25AE%2589%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E6%259D%25B1%25E8%2580%2583%25E5%25AF%259F-%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%258A%259B%25E5%2581%259A%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%259C%258B70%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2585%25B6%25E5%2585%25B8%25E5%25AE%2589%25E4%25BF%259D%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E7%25A9%25A9%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5HO%2BoULzyGumsBrFMfYiBSk%3D&h=604c0682\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/greaterchina/5d664409e60383421f678e41/%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E9%83%A8%E9%95%B7%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E8%80%83%E5%AF%9F-%E5%BC%B7%E8%AA%BF%E5%85%A8%E5%8A%9B%E5%81%9A%E5%A5%BD%E5%BB%BA%E5%9C%8B70%E5%B9%B4%E6%85%B6%E5%85%B8%E5%AE%89%E4%BF%9D%E7%B6%AD%E7%A9%A9%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C</a><br />\n<br />\n公安部部長趙克志前日在廣東考察，強調全力做好建國七十周年慶典的安保維穩工作，準確認識當前形勢，守好國家政治安全「南大門」。<br />\n<br />\n國務委員兼公安部部長趙克志周一到過廣州公安基層派出所，和廣東省公安廳指揮中心等地，檢查指導建國七十周年的安保維穩工作，並慰問前線公安民警和警務輔助人員。<br />\n<br />\n期間趙克志主持座談會，聽取公安機關工作匯報，他充分肯定廣東公安取得的顯著成績，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>強調要毫不動搖地堅持中共對公安工作的全面及絕對領導，始終在政治立場上，與中央保持高度一致。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n趙克志又指，要準確認識當前形勢和風險挑戰、嚴密防範及嚴厲打擊各類顛覆滲透破壞和暴力恐怖活動、堅決守好國家政治安全「南大門」、堅決捍衛國家政治安全，全力確保社會大局持續安全穩定，並深入開展全警實戰大練兵。<br />\n<br />\n另外，趙克志亦充分肯定廣東公安機關圍繞粵港澳大灣區建設，以大數據等技術，為港澳居民提供便利服務，希望可以進一步簡化，公安政務的行政程序。"},{"pid":"c27be77228c8c3c11290267dfbea2706c45019bd","tid":1513558,"uid":54337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:27:05.000Z","msg":"//強調要毫不動搖地堅持中共對公安工作的全面及絕對領導，始終在政治立場上，與中央保持高度一致。//<br />\n<br />\n党不嬲都指揮槍<br />\n而家香港地，槍指揮党<br />\n於共产党眼中，你們簡直係想篡党奪權<br />\n<br />\n你地班仆街衰撚硬"},{"pid":"e5865e52fa48fef99549b6d692f6b111e53f171e","tid":1513558,"uid":38494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:28:05.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">8.28 #Metoo 遮打花園</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">8.31 民陣遊行 直指中聯辦</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.01 機場 13:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.02 全港三罷</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今晚見</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></div>"},{"pid":"f8d1cd39a20b14990fa0b22c0dd8abc412b5b406","tid":1513558,"uid":77092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:28:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4397dc831c22c0c2375541f6bff639ab7487c528","tid":1513558,"uid":306807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:29:30.000Z","msg":"今晚十點一齊嗌五大訴求 同埋<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style